title: JPMorgan's Dimon Says Chipping Away at Fed Will Drive Rates Higher
description: JPMorgan Chase Chair and CEO Jamie Dimon weighs in on the independence of the Federal Reserve during an interview with David Rubenstein at the US Chamber of Commerce's 2026 State of American Business. (Source: Bloomberg)
